<https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/docs-databooks-stack-detection-md/interior> {
    <https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/docs-databooks-stack-detection-md> db:content """## Docker Base Image → Runtime

If no manifest file is present but a `Dockerfile` exists, the `FROM` line reveals the runtime:

| FROM line pattern | Runtime |
|------------------|---------|
| `FROM node:X` | Node.js X |
| `FROM python:X` | Python X |
| `FROM golang:X` | Go X |
| `FROM eclipse-temurin:X` | Java X (Eclipse Temurin JDK) |
| `FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:X` | .NET X |
| `FROM ruby:X` | Ruby X |
| `FROM rust:X` | Rust X |
| `FROM alpine` (alone) | Check what's installed via `RUN apk add` |









""" ;
        db:created "2026-04-18" ;
        db:hierarchy 3 ;
        db:id "stack-detection" ;
        db:layer "meta" ;
        db:scope "project" ;
        db:title "Stack Detection" ;
        db:transformer "human" ;
        db:type "plain-doc" ;
        db:version "0.1" ;
        oe:fileExt ".md" ;
        oe:fileName "stack-detection.md" ;
        oe:filePath "docs/databooks/stack-detection.md" ;
        oe:fileSizeBytes 5915 .
}

